# Project capability manager

Use only for missing or unhealthy dependencies, capability gaps, or explicit capability management.
Use Codex-native Skill discovery for ordinary tasks.

- Read [approved providers and capability gaps](references/capability-gaps.md).
- Follow the [quality and governance rules](references/quality-and-governance.md).
- Never start another Codex or delegate task execution to `vibe run`.
